  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you develop a sixth sense that helps you avoid traps. You gain a +2 bonus on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/perception\">Perception</a>&nbsp;checks made to notice traps. You also gain a +1 bonus on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Reflex\">Reflex</a>&nbsp;saves to avoid traps and a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Dodge-Bonus\">dodge bonus</a>&nbsp;to AC against attacks made by traps. These bonuses increase by +1 at 7th level and for every four&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/sorcerer\">sorcerer</a>&nbsp;levels you gain thereafter (to a maximum of +5 at 19th level). This bonus stacks with that provided by a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/rogue\">rogueâ€™s</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/rogue#TOC-Trap-Sense-Ex-\">trap sense</a>&nbsp;and similar abilities.</p>",
